ActBroadcasting Act
SubjectCanadian Broadcasting Corporation **LEASING AGREEMENT**
PrecisOrder authorizing the Canadian Broadcasting Corporation to enter into a lease agreement with DIALOG ONTARIO INC., as tenant to lease a portion of the real property at 250 Front Street West in Toronto, Ontario, and to grant in favour of DIALOG ONTARIO INC., an option to renew the lease for one further period of five years.
